{"tid":108594,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"【無骨氣開箱】PS4用滑鼠 Venom X4","createTime":"2017-02-05T11:17:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-05T18:24:08.000Z","uid":3350,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1ac89d3c4074d490c0b48a9316b4d6c7baccb2b0","tid":108594,"uid":3350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T11:17:43.000Z","msg":"我知道一定有巴打鬧我無用無骨氣，但我呢d打工仔，<br />\n做到三更半夜先返屋企，只係想安安樂樂打陣機，<br />\n但手制用得太屎，於是買ps4用嘅mouse。<br />\n<br />\n早前買過hori tac g1。set極都唔順，我估係我唔識set，<br />\n但又唔想浪費時間去set，須知打機一刻值千金，<br />\nSet得嚟都已經要瞓，所以好無骨氣咁上網買呢套Venom X4。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ajH0aM5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FajH0aM5.jpg&h=b2103aea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個盒嘅設計唔只簡單，係醜！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NAx24ow.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNAx24ow.jpg&h=a990afee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n裡面包咁多嘢。個手制係無線，不過mouse就係有線，好怪嘅設計。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2sW50m0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2sW50m0.jpg&h=49f4c7e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n駁呢舊嘢去ps4，但另方面又要駁個ps4手制，咁先用得。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F190DoR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF190DoR.jpg&h=944866a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個mouse明抄Logitech<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n後記：<br />\n可以用電腦或手機做setting，不過唔知點解電腦set唔到制，<br />\n唔想徙時間，於是試用手機，都搞好耐先connect到，<br />\n不過就成功set到。<br />\n<br />\n試用後好過tac g1太多！d人話g1 set好有電腦九成手感，<br />\n我覺得venom直頭95%以上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過個價差唔多係g1一倍，其實好貴。<br />\n<br />\n另外，venom 可以駁第三方keyboard、mouse，<br />\n但我懶去試⋯<br />\n<br />\n再講一次：我知我無用，打機廢但又要打，請各位巴打原諒，<br />\n有緣打機遇上，唔好唔同我玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c97fcb1268aa6e4aba0f2ba77be669cdf37e205f","tid":108594,"uid":2646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T16:23:34.000Z","msg":"我用過上一代，非常好用，我最近都買左hori新個個系列，係真係好難用<br />\n但都係唔習慣d制，想賣返出去"},{"pid":"e4d1dfacce757f4bac4a8e191e3e6ddaac5dcbdc","tid":108594,"uid":35393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T17:48:01.000Z","msg":"有無用過aten phantom-s ?"},{"pid":"5a57f4a9c830554a1aff626ee6da5aafee90ce06","tid":108594,"uid":52023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T17:50:55.000Z","msg":"拎隻mouse返去destiny/bf1玩pvp一定大殺三方<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8f3b4c79b44dc6b534cdb654c391c67a4642b7f","tid":108594,"uid":2646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T18:24:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無用過aten phantom-s ?</blockquote><br />\n用過， venom好用d"}]}